# QA / device-dump assets — local working files, not repo content (curated numbered
# listing screenshots under docs/screenshots/NN_*.png stay tracked)
/docs/screenshots/Screenshot_*.jpg
/docs/screenshots/[0-9][0-9]/
/docs/screenshots/*.mp4
/docs/play-store-feature-images/
/docs/qa-report-*.md

